---
// This is the Astro Component frontmatter.
// No JavaScript logic needed here for the slideshow.
---

<style>
  /* flattened media queries (valid CSS) */
  .mainDiv h2 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 2.25rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 780px) {
    .mainDiv h2 {
      font-size: 2.75rem;
      line-height: 4.25rem;
      text-align: left;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 990px) {
    .imageTesti {
      display: none;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1200px) {
    .mainDiv h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1400px) {
    .mainDiv h2 {
      font-size: 3.7rem;
    }
  }
</style>

<div
  class="w-screen flex justify-center"
  data-scroll-speed="1"
  data-scroll
  data-scroll-offset="100"
>
  <div class="bg-white w-[80%] py-6 font-san mainDiv">
    <h2 class="text-[1.5rem]
text-[#474747] mb-10">Our Values</h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-16 max-w-5xl">
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-light">
        "The Principles That Power Our Progress"
      </p>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed font-light">
        But with projects to deliver and timelines to keep in check, who has got
        your back to keep scanning and saving on what you dish out every month?
        **Stable.**
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div
  class="font-sans py-10"
  data-scroll-speed="1"
  data-scroll
  data-scroll-offset="100"
>
  <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 md:space-x-6">
    <div class="w-full">
      <div
        class="flex flex-col md:flex-row slide-item max-w-7xl mx-auto shadow-xl rounded-2xl overflow-hidden"
      >
        <div
          class="flex imageTesti items-center justify-center p-8 md:p-16 mr-6 bg-[#f5f4fb] rounded-2xl w-full md:w-1/3 min-h-[250px]"
        >
          [Image of Testimonial Icon 2]
        </div>

        <div
          class="flex flex-col justify-center p-8 md:p-16 bg-[#f5f4fb] rounded-2xl w-full md:w-full"
        >
          <blockquote
            class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-normal text-gray-600 leading-snug mb-6"
          >
            “In less than a month, we saved thousands of dollars (23%) of our
            total AWS bill.”
          </blockquote>
          <div class="text-sm">
            <p class="font-semibold text-violet-700 mb-0">Alexandre Walsh</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
              Co-Founder & Engineering VP, @ Nexapp and Axify
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="flex flex-col md:flex-row slide-item max-w-7xl mx-auto shadow-xl rounded-2xl overflow-hidden"
        style="display: none;"
      >
        <div
          class="flex items-center justify-center p-8 md:p-16 mr-6 bg-[#f5f4fb] rounded-2xl w-full md:w-1/3 min-h-[250px]"
        >
        </div>
        <div
          class="flex flex-col justify-center p-8 md:p-16 bg-[#f5f4fb] rounded-2xl w-full md:w-2/3"
        >
          <blockquote
            class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-normal text-gray-600 leading-snug mb-6"
          >
            “Using Stable, we saw an immediate 15% reduction in our EC2 spend.”
          </blockquote>
          <div class="text-sm">
            <p class="font-semibold text-violet-700 mb-0">Jane Doe</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Engineering Manager, @ CloudCo</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="flex space-x-2 mt-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-0">
    <button
      class="w-7 prev h-7 flex items-center justify-center bg-black text-white rounded-xl transition-colors hover:bg-gray-700"
    >
      <svg
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        class="w-5 h-5"
        fill="none"
        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        stroke="currentColor"
      >
        <path
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          stroke-width="2"
          d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path>
      </svg>
    </button>
    <button
      class="w-7 h-7 next flex items-center justify-center bg-black text-white rounded-xl transition-colors hover:bg-gray-700"
    >
      <svg
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        class="w-5 h-5"
        fill="none"
        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        stroke="currentColor"
      >
        <path
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          stroke-width="2"
          d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
      </svg>
    </button>
  </div>
</div>
<script src="../scripts/slideshow.js"></script>
